trans-unit.source: Represents Digital Rights Management (DRM) information that is stored in an <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerar Digital Rights Management (DRM) information som lagras i en <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: RightsManagementInformation provides access to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> and <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> data stored in a rights managed protected <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>.
trans-unit.target: RightsManagementInformation ger åtkomst till <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>och <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>data som lagras i ett rättigheter hanteras skyddade <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"></xref> for accessing the package's encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"> </xref> för att komma åt paketet är krypterad dataström för rights management.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"></xref> for accessing the rights management information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"> </xref> för åtkomst till hanteringsinformation rättigheter.

trans-unit.source: Deletes the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> for a specified user from the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Tar bort den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> för en viss användare från dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: The user of the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> to be deleted.
trans-unit.target: Användare av den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> som ska tas bort.

trans-unit.source: Returns a dictionary collection of user and <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> key/value pairs from the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en ordlista samling och <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> nyckel/värde-par från dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: GetEmbeddedUseLicenses only returns those use licenses that are currently embedded in the package.
trans-unit.target: GetEmbeddedUseLicenses returnerar bara de licenser som för närvarande är inbäddade i paketet.

trans-unit.source: It does not include any other use licenses that the application might have acquired separately from a rights management server but that are not yet embedded in the package.
trans-unit.target: Det innehåller inte någon annan användning licenser som programmet kan erhållit separat från en rights management-server men som ännu inte är inbäddade i paketet.

trans-unit.source: A collection of user and <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> key/value pairs that are contained in the rights managed protected package.
trans-unit.target: En samling av användare och <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> nyckel/värde-par som ingår i de rättigheter som hanteras skyddade paketet.

trans-unit.source: Returns the embedded <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref> from the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar den inbäddade <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"> </xref> från dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: The embedded <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref>; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if the package does not contain a <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den inbäddade <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"> </xref>; eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, om paketet inte innehåller en <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The rights management information in this package cannot be read by the current version of this class.
trans-unit.target: Rights management information i det här paketet kan inte läsas av den aktuella versionen av den här klassen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a specified user's embedded <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> from the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en angiven användare har inbäddade <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> från dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: The user or user group to return the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> for.
trans-unit.target: Användaren eller användargruppen för att returnera den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> för.

trans-unit.source: The for the specified user; or , if the package does not contain a that matches the given userKey.
trans-unit.target: Den för den angivna användaren; eller , om paketet inte innehåller en som matchar de angivna userKey .

trans-unit.source: The userKey parameter is .
trans-unit.target: The userKey parameter is .

trans-unit.source: The rights management information in this package cannot be read by the current version of this class.
trans-unit.target: Rights management information i det här paketet kan inte läsas av den aktuella versionen av den här klassen.

trans-unit.source: Saves a given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"></xref> to the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Sparar en given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense"> </xref> till dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> can contain only one <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>kan endast innehålla en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>

trans-unit.source: Each call to SavePublishLicense will overwrite any prior <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> contained in the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.
trans-unit.target: Varje anrop till SavePublishLicense kommer att skriva över eventuella tidigare <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>som ingår i <xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.EncryptedPackageEnvelope> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>

trans-unit.source: The publish license to store and embed in the package.
trans-unit.target: Publiceringslicensen att lagra och bädda in i paketet.

trans-unit.source: The publishLicense parameter is .
trans-unit.target: The publishLicense parameter is .

trans-unit.source: The rights management information in this package cannot be read by the current version of this class.
trans-unit.target: Rights management information i det här paketet kan inte läsas av den aktuella versionen av den här klassen.

trans-unit.source: Saves a given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> for a specified user to the encrypted rights management data stream.
trans-unit.target: Sparar en given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> för en angiven användare till dataströmmen krypterade rights management.

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> for the specified user has been saved, it can be retrieved through the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.LoadUseLicense%2A> method and from the collection returned by <xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.GetEmbeddedUseLicenses%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Efter den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>för den angivna användaren har sparats, de kan hämtas via den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.LoadUseLicense%2A>metoden och från en samling som returneras av <xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.GetEmbeddedUseLicenses%2A>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.GetEmbeddedUseLicenses%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.RightsManagementInformation.LoadUseLicense%2A> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> can store the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> rights information for multiple content users.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>kan lagra den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>rights information för flera användare för innehåll.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: Each ContentUser can have at most one <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>.
trans-unit.target: Varje ContentUser kan ha maximalt ett <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: If SaveUseLicense is called to store a new <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> for a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser> that already has a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>, the previous license will be overwritten with the new license.
trans-unit.target: Om SaveUseLicense anropas för att lagra en ny <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>för en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser>som redan har en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>, tidigare licens kommer att skrivas över med den nya licensen.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.ContentUser> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: The user of the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Användare av den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The use license to store and embed in the package.
trans-unit.target: Den här processen att lagra och bädda in i paketet.

trans-unit.target: Either the userKey or useLicense parameter is .
